          "_name": "features1",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"features25\" group=\"Features\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showMainTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showMainSubtitle\">\n        <header>Card</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Icons\" name=\"showIcon\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Icon Color\" name=\"iconColor\" value=\"#f97316\" selected condition=\"showIcon\">\n        <select title=\"Columns\" name=\"columns\">\n            <option value=\"3\">4</option>\n            <option value=\"4\">3</option>\n            <option value=\"6\" selected>2</option>\n            <option value=\"12\">1</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background4.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#f4f6f8\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://vimeo.com/428046504\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row mb-5\">\n            <div class=\"col-12\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle || showMainSubtitle\">\n                <h3 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-2\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showMainTitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\">\n                    <b>Features</b>\n                </h3>\n                <h5 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style align-center mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showMainSubtitle\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\">\n                    List main features of your project in this block\n                </h5>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"row\">\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-center\">\n                    <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbri-delivery\" style=\"font-size: 200px;\"></span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b>Serwis awaryjny (on-demand)</b></h5>\n                    <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">Szybka reakcja w przypadku awarii maszyn, instalacji lub systemów automatyki.<br><br><b>Zakres:</b><br>- diagnostyka problemu<br>- naprawa awarii<br>- przywrócenie produkcji<br>- wsparcie techniczne<br><br><b>Dla kogo:</b><br>Firmy bez stałego wsparcia technicznego lub wymagające szybkiej reakcji.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-center\">\n                    <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                        <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbrib-file\" style=\"font-size: 200px;\"></span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b>Współpraca B2B (umowa serwisowa)</b></h5>\n                    <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">Stała współpraca w oparciu o umowę serwisową z określonym SLA.<br><br><b>Zakres:</b><br>- priorytetowa obsługa<br>- gwarantowany czas reakcji<br>- wsparcie techniczne<br>- przeglądy okresowe<br><br><b>Tryby:</b><br>- tylko usuwanie awarii<br>- serwis + prewencja<br>- pełna obsługa techniczna</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-center\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbrib-setting3\" style=\"font-size: 200px;\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b>Stała współpraca UR (utrzymanie ruchu)</b></h5>\n                        <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">Dedykowane wsparcie dla działu utrzymania ruchu.<br><br><b>Zakres:</b><br>- bieżące naprawy<br>- analiza awarii<br>- optymalizacja pracy maszyn<br>- wsparcie zespołu UR<br><br><b>Model:</b><br>👉 współpraca ciągła / abonament</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-center\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-users mobi-mbri\" style=\"font-size: 200px;\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b>Dedykowany zespół techniczny</b></h5>\n                        <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">Oddelegowanie zespołu specjalistów do zakładu klienta.<br><br><b>Zakres:</b><br>- stała obecność na obiekcie<br>- szybka reakcja<br>- pełne wsparcie produkcji<br>- integracja z zespołem klienta</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-center\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbri-setting\" style=\"font-size: 200px;\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b>Outsourcing techniczny</b></h5>\n                        <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">Przejęcie całości lub części procesów technicznych w zakładzie.<br><br><b>Zakres:</b><br>- utrzymanie ruchu<br>- automatyka<br>- elektryka<br>- zarządzanie serwisem<br><br><b>Korzyści:</b><br>✔ redukcja kosztów<br>✔ dostęp do specjalistów<br>✔ brak konieczności zatrudniania</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-center\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mobi-mbri-to-local-drive mobi-mbri\" style=\"font-size: 200px;\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b>Wdrożenia jednorazowe</b></h5>\n                        <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">Realizacja projektów technicznych i modernizacji.<br><br><b>Zakres:</b><br>- modernizacja linii produkcyjnych<br>- wdrożenie automatyki<br>- programowanie PLC<br>- uruchomienia systemów<br>- montaże</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-center\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbri-speed\" style=\"font-size: 200px;\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b>Obsługa techniczna instalacji</b></h5>\n                        <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">Kompleksowe utrzymanie instalacji technicznych.<br><br><b>Zakres:</b><br>- instalacje elektryczne<br>- systemy automatyki<br>- infrastruktura techniczna</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-center\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbri-bulleted-list\" style=\"font-size: 200px;\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b>Przeglądy techniczne</b></h5>\n                        <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">Regularne i doraźne kontrole stanu technicznego.<br><br><b>Typy:</b><br>- przeglądy okresowe<br>- przeglądy prewencyjne<br>- audyty techniczne<br>- kontrole poawaryjne</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div><div class=\"item features-without-image mb-5 col-12 col-md-{{columns}}\">\n                <div class=\"item-wrapper align-center\">\n                    <div class=\"card-box\">\n                        <div class=\"iconfont-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showIcon\">\n                            <span mbr-icon class=\"mbr-iconfont mbri-home\" style=\"font-size: 200px;\"></span>\n                        </div>\n                        <h5 class=\"card-title mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\" data-app-selector=\".card-title, .iconfont-wrapper\"><b>Generalny wykonawca techniczny</b></h5>\n                        <p class=\"card-text mbr-fonts-style mb-0\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".card-text\">Kompleksowa realizacja inwestycji przemysłowych.<br><br><b>Zakres:</b><br>- ustawianie i uruchamianie maszyn<br>- instalacje elektryczne<br>- systemy automatyki<br>- integracja systemów<br>- przygotowanie zakładu do produkcji<br><br>Model:<br>👉 „pod klucz”</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
          "_cid": "vf3SonqyYJ",
          "_anchor": "features1-bi",
          "_protectedParams": [],
          "_global": false,
          "_once": false,
          "_params": {}
        },
        {
          "alias": false,
          "_styles": {
            "& when not (@fullScreen)": {
              "padding-top": "(@paddingTop * 1rem)",
              "padding-bottom": "(@paddingBottom * 1rem)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'image')": {
              "background-image": "url(@bg-value)"
            },
            "& when (@bg-type = 'color')": {
              "background-color": "@bg-value"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image.disabled": {
              "display": "none"
            },
            ".mbr-fallback-image": {
              "display": "block",
              "background-size": "cover",
              "background-position": "center center",
              "width": "100%",
              "height": "100%",
              "position": "absolute",
              "top": "0",
              "& when (@bg-type = 'video')": {
                "background-image": "url(@fallBackImage)"
              }
            },
            ".mbr-section-title": {
              "color": "#0f2a44",
              "text-align": "left"
            },
            ".mbr-section-subtitle": {
              "color": "#0f2a44",
              "text-align": "left"
            },
            ".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn": {
              "color": "#1f2933",
              "text-align": "left"
            }
          },
          "_name": "header3",
          "_sourceTheme": "mobirise5",
          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"header3\" group=\"Headers\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"10\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n\n        <input type=\"range\" inline name=\"textWidth\" title=\"Width\" min=\"4\" max=\"12\" value=\"12\" step=\"1\">\n        <select title=\"Align\" name=\"contentAlign\">\n            <option value selected>Left</option>\n            <option value=\"justify-content-center\">Center</option>\n            <option value=\"justify-content-end\">Right</option>\n        </select>\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/stara%20tablica-2000x3000.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#ffffff\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Video\" value=\"https://youtu.be/R371R8FOIGc\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background13.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\" checked>\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#0f2a44\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.7\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div class=\"align-center\" mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row {{contentAlign}}\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-{{textWidth}}\">\n                <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><b>Dobierz model współpracy do swoich potrzeb</b><div><b><br></b></div></h1>\n                <h2 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-3\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubitle\"><br><b>Potrzeba klienta&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Model</b></h2>\n                <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showText\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .mbr-section-btn\">________________________________________________________________________________<br>Sporadyczne awarie&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Serwis awaryjny<br>________________________________________________________________________________\n<br>Stałe wsparcie&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Umowa B2B<br>________________________________________________________________________________\n<br>Wsparcie UR&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Stała współpraca<br>\n________________________________________________________________________________\n<br>Brak zespołu technicznego&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;Outsourcing<br>\n________________________________________________________________________________\n<br>Nowa inwestycja&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Generalny wykonawca<br></p>\n                <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\" class=\"mbr-section-btn mt-3\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\"><a class=\"btn btn-success\" href=\"https://mobiri.se\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\">Free Download!</a></div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
